. On the contrary, for the EOSs with quark\ndeconfinement we get M_crit =~ M^N_max > 2M_sun, which reconciles SN1987A and\nPSR J0751+1807.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 31 May 2007 13:12:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-06-01"}
